---
title: Kushiyaki Skewer Party with Steak, Pork Meatballs, Shishitos, Cuke Salad & Rice
description: Kushiyaki—a Japanese dish of skewered and grilled meat and vegetables—is kind of the ultimate party food, and here, you'll be making two kinds. For one, you'll pair marinated steak with shishito peppers. For the other, you'll layer savory pork meatballs with tomatoes, and more shishitos. Cucumber salad, rice, and a double shot of dippers (stir-fry sauce and katsu mayo) complete the meal!
